{"tid":1866684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抽獎？2盒thx？瞓撚醒未？","createTime":"2020-02-06T23:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T04:23:25.000Z","uid":239413,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4db625b218c25f6b1dcf4e3e55eb576a7693da26","tid":1866684,"uid":239413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:42:02.000Z","msg":"係呀，繼上一次抽機票、iPhone之後，宜家又抽啦，抽咩？口罩呀！<br />\n<br />\n一係平時po生活照既帳無啦啦會搞抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLZGKKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLZGKKg.png&h=fb403092&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUqyAQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUqyAQX.png&h=f9270315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一係開個新帳一黎就話抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15BRnv4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15BRnv4.png&h=b536d9a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rza3dCL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRza3dCL.png&h=2db3e844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內容又係叫你follow, like, comment &amp; share<br />\n都睇到厭，我都唔想以已之心度人之腹，佢地連點樣抽、幾時抽既詳情都冇講，但又好神奇地有幾千幾萬個人去癲埋一份<br />\n<br />\n我知，好多連登仔都知，佢地咪又係用假抽獎黎呃followers，但係呢幾日打開ig，見到唔少認識既人係度share story, tag呢個tag果個，真係好無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚心你地啦，咪貪呢啲抽獎啦，經一事都唔長一智，見到「話」有口罩就搶住含、搶住奶，瘋狂送data比人，都唔知做乜<br />\n<br />\n雖然落街排同上網搶都好難買到，但係我想講呢啲抽獎係100%抽唔到呀。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8455cd360b6d394203a6d1ef8a72b72c1794573c","tid":1866684,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:56:04.000Z","msg":"兩盒 Thx"},{"pid":"a74f6854ed64e18e06871fc594ce8d253bdec5c8","tid":1866684,"uid":282374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23: